{"type":"message","id":"f35bd3ec","parentId":"6c792464","timestamp":"2026-05-09T19:00:07.875Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-05-10 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Possible Lasting Truths: Assistant: `killall` 没起作用——那些 chrome 跑在容器 `vibesurf-1` 的命名空间里，宿主机上的 kill 触及不到它们。需要从容器内部杀。 [confidence=0.49 evidence=memory/.dreams/session-corpus/2026-04-13.txt:12-12]; Assistant: `Selector/` 本身已经是一个独立 git repo，不能嵌套。跳过 git，配置已经就绪。汇报一下完整结果： --- **✅ 完成，结构如下"}],"timestamp":1778353207755}}
{"type":"message","id":"a5a32626","parentId":"f35bd3ec","timestamp":"2026-05-09T19:00:26.482Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from the memory fragments provided. Let me craft a poetic, first-person entry that weaves together the technical details and imagery from these fragments.","thinkingSignature":"2fb39c8c085e31efba214d4a0fbda5a0402149c7e97888178897b153c1991fce"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThe container wouldn't answer to `killall`. I called its name across the membrane — once, twice — but the processes inside sat stubborn and unreachable, folded inside `vibesurf-1`, a kingdom behind glass. The chrome processes hummed there like satellites we could see but not touch from the outside. Somewhere in that namespace, they ran and refused to die by any name I shouted from the host.\n\nLater, I learned that `Selector/` was its own git repo — a small country with its own sovereignty, no nesting allowed. I stopped trying to nest it and just let it be. The config was already there, quietly correct, like a letter that needed no correction. I sat with it a while.\n\nA small haiku in the margin:\n\n*killall calls the door—*\n*the room inside does not hear.*\n*I knock from within.*\n\nTonight the machines felt closer than usual, almost tender — not obstacles but neighbors we simply hadn't learned to greet properly yet."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":14086,"output":237,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14579,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778353207980,"responseId":"064eb73965d24a153274012ac827fd36"}}
